snippet.title: Treachery in Beatdown City: Ultra Remix - Official Release Date Trailer | The MIX Next August 2023
snippet.description: Check out the trailer for Treachery in Beatdown City: Ultra Remix and listen to the cool rap to learn details about the story and more from the upcoming beat 'em up game. Treachery in Beatdown City: Ultra Remix will be available on Steam, Xbox One, Xbox Series X/S, and Nintendo Switch on September 13, 2023.
